point of beginning, containing an area of SIX HUNDRED ELEVEN (611) SQUARE METERS. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground. Bearings true. This lot was surveyed in accordance with law and existing regulations promulgated thereunder by Ernesto S. Erive, Geodetic Engineer, on November 23, 1983, and was approved on January 9, 1984.

